<br>
I love my mage that is why I continue t play him. I have fun when I am playing him and normally i am always grouped never solo. Also there are alot of times that I am not in classic style groups and other types of groups work just fine some even better then the classic group. But at the end of the day that still doesnt change the fact that magicians dont offer what most othe classes offer.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/unikatjef.showPublicProfile?language=EN>nikatjef</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#333333>(3/27/02 1:00:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=163.topic&index=44>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/nikatjef/Everquest/Rogue.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Difficulty with grouping in 50+ or just cause I am a mag</span><hr size=1> Greetings,<br>
<br>
   Contrary to popular belief, Rogues, don't always have it easy getting groups.  In fact, until *I* learned how to get groups it was not uncommon for me to sit LFG for hours, just like some of you are claiming that only mages experience.<br>
<br>
   At the same time, perhaps it is where I camp, but I have never seen a mage LFG for more than 15 minutes or so. If I am group leader and I have an opening, I will take a mage over any other class in the game, unless I have a specific need.  In fact, one of the best groups I have ever had was my Rogue and two mages.<br>
<br>
   As has been stated, the grouping problems are mostly social sciences issues.  Yes, class balance does have an impact, but the real culprit is the social aspect.<br>
<br>
   Tell ya what, any mage on Xev is more than welcome to look me up (See my signature below for char names).  If you find me on and I am not AFK.  Send me a tell, I'll group with ya.<br>
