Off topic some. I will say that &quot;Classic Group&quot; was a term coined to simply show the group that is the most popular. If the world of Norrath were very different and there were enough content to support unlimited AE groups, that would be the classic group. The point of defining the most often created group, and showing that there are fewer spots available in that group for Mages than other classes (which you agreed with) it still shows that Class (role) does have an impact on getting into a group.<br>
